        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository a4a2e646-b45e-427a-9cb6-0a297f5293a3).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. \r\rIt has been brought to our attention that Ether has been working on a new virus after seizing all the research on the Nightshade virus under the Carlisle estate. Ether has been hard at work in their lab under The Villa Caruso, reverse engineering the virus, in hopes of creating a bioweapon to auction off to the highest bidder. We can&apos;t allow this to happen. Infiltrate the mansion and eliminate Ether&apos;s top researchers on the project, as well as the virus. \r\rBest of luck, 47",
